snippet.textDisplay: Gaan ta onekeri valo lagse oneeek bujhlam. But taste differs from person to person. Ekta gaan er moddhe asman theke jomin porjonto sob include kora ki khub joruri! Eto different type er musical instruments+ different types er sur+ sammano koyek line gaan = joga khichuri I think. For example 1:57 theek 2:47 porjonto just music!! Ei music part gula baad dile je part gula pore thake ta ekta arektar sathe sur er dik theke bemanan. Ha ekadhik sur niye combination kora jai jemon coke studio er onno gaan gulai best combinations ase, but ei tai sobkisu include korte giye tal harai felse. General mass jokhon mukhe mukhe or addar majhe gaan ta gaibe tokhon tara music sara kintu just lines gula gai, jeita korekta few lines, jar moddhe repeat + meye duita je part ta gailo tar sathe baki part gulo sur e kemne mil khai ami bujhina, jai hok nizer kase jemon laglo tai bollam arki
